High school student voting rights should be abolished. High voting rights, which certain political forces make schools political and students political instruments, should be reconsidered. According to the Framework Act on Education, education should not be used as a means to spread political partisan or personal prejudice Students must not guide or instigate students to support or oppose a particular political party or faction. It is in conflict with the Civil Act, which specifies that a person is an adult and prohibits him from performing legally effective acts alone until the age of life. As such, it is necessary to discuss the revision of laws and to come up with measures to resolve the side effects and confusion caused by the adjustment of the age of majority. It's one thing to do. Don't politicize the students. Make sure that you don't politicize the students. Make sure that you do character education so that you don't have boys. The size of the market is returning to before the spread of the new coronavirus Corona as the initial public offering of the preliminary listed companies with the smallest total for the first time in years is shrinking. According to the Korea Exchange, the total amount of public offerings of newly listed stocks in last month was counted as 100 million won, which is the smallest since last month's won in the early stages of the spread of the corona virus. The public offering market this year is on a gradual downward trend. With the listing of Energy Solution at the beginning of the year, the domino public offering was expected to be successful, but the market has been shrinking for several months. The industry has cited the delisting of Daeeos as the first reason that the public offering market has entered a cooling period in the first half of this year. OneStore tried to enter the KOSPI, but withdrew because the competition rate for institutional demand forecasting did not meet expectations. He explained that the stock price of companies has been sluggish since the listing and explained that the trend of more conservative analysis of profitability and growth potential is strong in the process. According to Anta Securities, the total operating profit forecast for this year of Kakao Bank, Kakao Pay Krafton, an energy solution listed in 2018, was downgraded from KRW trillion in the beginning of the month to KRW trillion in the month. If the downward revision of the operating profit forecast for Korea continues, the uncertainty felt by investors about the newly listed companies will increase. However, the market stagnation is expected to continue for a while as preliminary IPO stocks are delaying the IPO in consideration of market conditions rather than efforts to set the IPO price. The issue is that Socar Curly Oasis K-Bank and others postponed their listing schedule, and a drought is expected in the public offering market in the second half of the year. He said that if he subscribes to individual investors before making a decision, he can review the needs of individual investors as well, so an appropriate public offering will help him decide.

Gaekao employees' opinions gathered Kakao's ambitious metaverse working system was revised after many controversies Through an internal notice on the last day, it was announced that the working methods of the Metaverse work system, voice channel connection and weekly offline meetings, were changed from mandatory to recommended. Previously, Kakao announced a metaverse work system last month that allows people to work regardless of work location, from city to city. He emphasized that he could be connected to the channel in real time and communicate with his colleagues. CEO Nam Goong-hoon also said that he would support the metaverse work system centered on the connection to help crews work efficiently and establish a culture that penetrates the Kakao community. After the announcement of the metaverse work system, it faced harsh criticism from employees. It is argued that the system is a work system with the characteristics of a circular prison designed to manage a large number of prisoners as a watcher of a small number of Panopticon in the past. It is pointed out that the method of having to turn on or wear bone conduction earphones is excessive. CEO Namgoong-hoon hastily took action. He announced his intention to review it last month. After testing the voice communication tool for a certain period of time, employees voted directly by organizational unit or functional unit, which was mandatory. This decision is interpreted as a result of accepting such internal opinions. A Kakao official said that only the ground rules, the working rules, have been changed, and that the metaverse work system is being maintained. The nolgeum system is introduced every other week, and if implemented, it is expected to be applied from next month. The introduction of an in-house restaurant is also under discussion. As prices around Pangyo are high, employees are in the mood for a restaurant. Kakao An official said that the implementation of the in-house restaurant system is expected to be decided while observing the progress after the introduction of the metaverse work system.

This is possible because the timing of the sell order and the actual settlement time of stocks are different. Short selling uses this time difference to secure a cheaper quantity than the time of the sell order. First, the quantity waiting for the simultaneous call is concluded in the order of price time quantity, so we wait for a large number of purchases before loading. Second priority buy, we make a short sale to reach the lowest point to be signed. Fill in the asking price In short selling, as much as the buying volume has been digested, the surrendered property that exceeds the initial volume must be accumulated at the upper quote price. What is clear is that short selling must also be repaid when the actual settlement is reached. Currently, short selling does not receive as much surrendered property as the initial amount handed over. Web Board Game Regulations Japan's Cabinet Council Passed Web Board Game Regulations A Little Breathtaking Reporter Name Won-bin Moon Reporter Input Correction Payment Limit Increase of 10,000 Won Increase Expectations for Sales Growth in Industry Passed by the State Council Web Board Game in Google Play Service Google Play Services A bill to raise the monthly payment limit of web board games from 10,000 won to 10,000 won passed the Cabinet meeting in Japan Good news of sales recovery is expected in related industries that have been hurt by long-standing regulations. The bill is a partial amendment to the Enforcement Decree of the Game Industry Promotion Act. The key is to raise the limit on the purchase of game money for web board games by 10,000 won from the existing 10,000 won to 10,000 won. There is also a content that clarifies the phrase “No” and specifies the compliance with the measures to protect users and prevent speculative game products made in consultation with the Game Management Committee. There are no obstacles considering The limit started at 10,000 won and rose to 10,000 won per year. The limit on work loss, which was limited to 10,000 won, was abolished every year. This regulation is a sunset type and is reviewed every year. According to the Korea Game Industry Association, the domestic web board game market, which exceeded 100 million won, plummeted to the level of 100 million won a year. The market was split in half under the name of speculation concerns The web board game industry is expected to benefit from easing. When the monthly payment limit was raised last year, it is estimated that the web board game industry had an increase in sales to a certain extent. The web board game industry said that it expects an increase in the index. While we welcome the passage of the State Council, we are wary of whether speculative issues will arise. A web board game company has complied with the amendment as it aims to rationally adjust related regulations by reflecting the growth trend of the game industry. Reporter Won-bin Moon, who said that he would make continuous efforts for the even growth of the industry.

Prospects for benefit from web board game companies Raised the payment limit by 10,000 won Cabinet meeting Expected to increase sales in the industry Passing the Cabinet Meeting Prospects to benefit from web board game companies Web board game regulations took a little breather Reporter Moon Won-bin Corrected the input of reporters Raised the payment limit by 10,000 won Cabinet meeting Expectations for increased sales in the passing industry Web board game on Google Play service Web board game on Google Play service Web board game A bill to raise the monthly payment limit from 10,000 won to 10,000 won was passed by the Cabinet of Ministers in Japan Good news of sales recovery is expected in the industry. It is the first time in a year that the monthly purchase limit has been revised. The feasibility of the regulation is reviewed every other year as a year-end regulation. After the increase, it remained at the same place for a year. The web board game industry has been constantly seeking for deregulation, but the Game Management Committee did not accept it. It is implemented after collecting opinions by the first day of the month. As it is an enforcement ordinance, not a law, it is only necessary to pass the procedures such as the review of the Ministry of Legislation and the cabinet meeting of the Vice Ministers after the notice of legislation. The industry is also cautiously predicting the passage of the amendment. However, opposition from civic groups is a variable because of the need for an upgrade. Web board game companies are expected to benefit again after a year, and Web board game companies such as Neowiz are expected to benefit from the easing of regulations. If it goes up to 10,000 won, the payment limit per game will also increase from 10,000 won to 10,000 won. According to the enforcement rules, the payment limit per game must be within a month's worth. In fact, game sales have increased in the past due to deregulation. Hangame is running a website famous for its web board games. As the annual payment limit was raised from 10,000 won to 10,000 won, the game division's sales also increased from 100 million won to 100 million won. This was greatly shaken by the web board regulation every year Sales fell from 100 million won to 100 million won, and after that, the work loss limit was abolished in 2011. Neowiz's domestic game sales increased to 100 million won compared to the previous year. It is also noteworthy that the web board field has been a market where most game companies do not enter due to regulations. However, recently, as games that make money, also known as games, have received attention in the industry, several game companies are putting their power back into web board games. In order to preoccupy the emerging market, he has re-launched his specialty web board game.

Heads of fiscal, monetary and financial authorities gather to discuss macro-financial meeting Heads of fiscal, monetary and financial authorities decided to actively respond to concerns about growing uncertainty in the financial market after the Federal Open Market Committee of the US Federal Reserve (Fed) decided to raise the key interest rate. Deputy Prime Minister and Planning Minister of Finance Chang-yong Lee, Governor of the Bank of Korea, So-young Kim, Vice Chairman of the Financial Services Commission Lee Bok-hyeon, Chairman of the Financial Supervisory Service, Choi Sang-mok, Chief of Economic Affairs of the Presidential Office held an emergency macroeconomic and financial meeting at the Bank Hall in Seoul on the morning of the same day and discussed these issues. It has been open for the first time in a month and this is the first time under a new government. They say that there is a constant concern that the volatility of the international financial market will increase as concerns about an economic slowdown due to accelerated austerity tightening in the future. They diagnosed the current economic situation as a complex crisis as the prolonged Ukraine crisis and supply chain disruptions overlapped, and formed a consensus that difficulties would continue for a considerable period of time. Decided to actively cooperate to manage fluctuations in financial risk First of all, we shared a common perception that price stability is the most urgent issue. They take various measures, such as reducing the cost burden on the supply side and preventing the spread of expected inflation, while operating monetary policies that focus more on prices. He emphasized that he would strengthen his efforts. Regarding the financial and foreign exchange market, he said he would strengthen joint response efforts to prevent the spread of anxiety as uncertainty has increased. He explained that he would do his best not to exacerbate the phenomenon of crowding due to reactions. To this end, he said that he would make every effort to prevent systemic risks in advance by intensively examining the weak link between the soundness and liquidity of individual financial companies and the financial industry. surge in counter-trading is fueling the downtrend Investments made by individual investors in debt are fueling the stock market decline According to the Il Financial Investment Association, the daily average counter trading volume has recently exceeded 100 million won, showing a high level. This was the highest figure since last year. It was almost twice the daily average counter trades of 100 million won last year. In a situation where the stock market is showing great volatility, it is an analysis that a vicious cycle is appearing in which the stock price declines further as items for sale that did not pay off money or sell the stock in advance come to the market as a counter sale. It is structured to borrow money from a securities company to buy stocks and repay the money, but if the payment is not made within the trading day, a reverse transaction is made. According to the researcher, the number of counter-trading increases as the stock price declines continuously, and it is estimated that a vicious cycle occurs when the decline intensifies. The analysis explained that the increase in stock purchases through credit in the process of the stock price surge in the year when the Donghak ant craze blew after the novel coronavirus infection corona is acting as a burden in the process of the stock price decline. The stock price surged after the stock price plunged, so it is still at a high level compared to the pre-COVID level, both in absolute terms and relative to the market capitalization. As of the last day, the credit balance recorded a total of 100 billion won, including KRW trillion in the KOSPI and KRW trillion in the KOSDAQ. Analysts analyzed that the lack of incentives to buy at the trough and the increased selling pressure, including counter-trading, estimated that individual investors would have lost more than the current index after investing through credit loans. Researcher Choi said that it is possible that the inflows have been repaid before, but it is clear that the amount of inflows near the peak of the index is significant. If it occurs, he explained that there is a possibility that it will face a downtrend that exceeds the extent of fundamental damage due to selling pressure. The enormous amount of less than a trillion and a half is the amount that individual investors are estimated to have lost more than the current index after investing with credit loans.

As the KOSDAQ KOSPI KOSPI index recorded a decline this month and returned to the level at the time of the corona pandemic, it was pointed out that there is a debt investment behind the exceptionally large decline in the Korean stock market. It is considered to be a factor that puts a burden on the market, but it means that the burden of the credit transaction loan balance is limiting the overall rebound of the stock market due to supply and demand. This is because leveraged funds through credit transactions contribute to liquidity supply in a bull market, but trigger counter-trading in a bear market, adding to the downside risk of the market, such as a larger decline in stock prices of stocks with high credit balances, according to the Korea Exchange. The KOSPI ranks above the KOSDAQ for the decline rate among the world's leading stock market indexes from Monday to Sunday. This is in contrast to the large decline in the New York stock market during the same period. As for the reason why the stock market was particularly sluggish, the securities industry cited the size of debt investment. This is the size of the credit loan balance. The credit transaction loan balance of the KOSPI market was found to be at a level comparable to that of the KOSDAQ of the market capitalization. According to the historical pattern, the trend of the stock market rebounded only after a decrease in the credit loan balance was achieved. Heo Jae-wan, a researcher at Eugene Investment & Securities, said that most of the decline in stock prices last week came from counter-trading due to lack of margin. In the case of the domestic stock market, the total trading value of the stock market is decreasing due to a sharp drop in stock prices, while the credit balance ratio is showing a cascading decline. Ji-young Han, a researcher at Kiwoom Securities, said that the burden of credit transaction loan balances is limiting the overall stock market rebound. Analyzing that some of them were reinvested into the stock market and a surge in credit for related theme stocks during the monthly presidential election, one researcher said that additional stock market adjustments are needed to relieve the credit burden, resulting in a decrease in credit balance or macro-environmental uncertainty. As this eased, the stock market should rise and market capitalization should increase, but both are difficult to meet in a short period of time.
